thread.title: European air traffic warned over Syria strikes

title: European air traffic warned over Syria strikes
text:
European air traffic warned over Syria strikes 11:15am BST - 01:17 
Pan-European air traffic control agency Eurocontrol on Tuesday warned airlines to exercise caution in the eastern Mediterranean due to the possible launch of air strikes into Syria in next 72 hours. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
